  "5 kcal (a negligible trace amount of energy remaining after extensive metabolic losses)": "",
  "50 kcal (0.1% of the original: 50,000 x 0.1 x 0.1 x 0.1)": "",
  "500 kcal (1% of the original energy from the phytoplankton producer trophic level)": "",
  "Applying the 10% rule three times: producers (50,000) to primary consumers (5,000) to secondary consumers (500) to tertiary consumers (50 kcal). Only 0.1% of original energy reaches the fourth level.": "",
